feat: Implement dashboard page with sidebar navigation


This commit introduces a new dashboard page accessible to both candidates and recruiters.

  Key changes include:

- Dashboard Layout: A new layout for the dashboard section with a persistent sidebar.
- Sidebar Navigation: A reusable sidebar component with links for different user roles.
   - UI Components: Added new UI components for input, separator, sidebar,
      skeleton, and tooltip.
   - Styling: Updated global CSS to support the new dashboard layout.
   - Dependencies: Added @radix-ui/react-separator and
     @radix-ui/react-tooltip for enhanced UI.
